---
import site from '@/lib/site';
---

<section class="section s3-content">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="s3-content__layout">

      <div class="s3-content__body">
        <h2 class="s3-content__heading">Why Vitamin C Is The Ultimate Skin Brightening and Anti-Aging Treatment</h2>

        <h3 class="s3-content__subheading">Immediate Brightening and Glow</h3>
        <p class="s3-content__text">Our Vitamin C Facial begins with a professional microdermabrasion polish that removes dead skin cells and unclogs pores, instantly revealing brighter, smoother skin. We then apply a potent Vitamin C mask that floods your skin with antioxidants, creating an immediate luminosity and radiant glow you can see and feel right away.</p>

        <h3 class="s3-content__subheading">Powerful Collagen Boost and Anti-Aging</h3>
        <p class="s3-content__text">Vitamin C is one of the most scientifically-proven ingredients for stimulating collagen production. Our professional-grade formulations penetrate deeper than at-home products, activating your skin's natural collagen synthesis to firm and plump the skin, reduce the appearance of fine lines and wrinkles, and improve overall skin texture and elasticity.</p>

        <h3 class="s3-content__subheading">Safe and Gentle for All Skin Types</h3>
        <p class="s3-content__text">Unlike harsh chemical peels or aggressive laser treatments, our Vitamin C Facial is carefully formulated to be safe and effective for all skin types, including sensitive skin. There is no downtime required, you can return to your normal activities immediately after your treatment with a fresh, glowing complexion.</p>

        <h3 class="s3-content__subheading">Environmental Protection and Skin Health</h3>
        <p class="s3-content__text">Vitamin C is a powerful antioxidant that helps protect your skin from environmental damage caused by UV exposure, pollution, and free radicals. Our professional treatment creates a protective barrier that supports long-term skin health, helps fade dark spots and hyperpigmentation, and keeps your skin looking youthful and vibrant between sessions.</p>

        <div class="s3-content__cta">
          <a
            href={site.calcomUrl}
            class="btn btn--primary btn--lg"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >
            Schedule Today
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .s3-content__layout {
    max-width: var(--container-narrow);
    margin-inline: auto;
  }

  .s3-content__body {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .s3-content__heading {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-h2);
    font-weight: var(--weight-regular);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-xs);
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .s3-content__subheading {
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: var(--weight-bold);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: var(--space-xs) 0 0;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .s3-content__text {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .s3-content__cta {
    margin-top: var(--space-md);
  }
</style>
